svg.text: The data they collect comes from our interaction with the objects: your voice, your face, the map of your house and even your habits.
This data is not only stored by the company that produces the object -first party-, but also from other companies that are called second and third parties.

text.tspan: partner of the first party for hosting

svg.text: Smart objects are devices that have network connectivity and they work by collecting user data, process and analyse that data and then return it back to the user.
